Time Complexity: O(n)
Space Complexity: O(1)

Humne minsum ko initially INT_MAX set kiya tha.
Agar kabhi bhi koi valid subarray nahi mila jiska sum ≥ target,
to minsum kabhi update hi nahi hoga → wo INT_MAX hi rahega.
Us case me answer 0 dena hai (kyunki koi subarray mila hi nahi).

class Solution {
public:
    int minSubArrayLen(int target, vector<int>& nums) {
       int minsum = INT_MAX;
       int window = 0;
       int start = 0;

       for(int i=0; i<nums.size(); i++){
            window = window + nums[i];

            while(window >= target){
                minsum = min(minsum, i - start + 1);
                window = window - nums[start];
                start++;
            }
       }
       return (minsum == INT_MAX) ? 0 : minsum;
    }
};
